ActFisheries Act
PrecisRegulations amending the QUEBEC FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1990 AND CERTAIN OTHER FISHERIES REGULATIONS which, by simplifying and reducing the number of schedules, will make the Regulations easier to understand and enforce, improve the quality of service to the public and support the province's Paper Burden Reduction Initiative, effective April 1, 2009.
